title: ICE: rustdoc: unexpected const parent in type_of() / Const::from_anon_const: couldn't lit_to_const TypeError

labels.name: T-rustdoc
labels.description: Relevant to the rustdoc team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: requires-nightly
labels.description: This issue requires a nightly compiler in some way.
